###########################################
##### Organizer Application Generator  ####
##### Version 1.0                      ####
###########################################

script/generate organizer_application [application_name] [description] [icon-cls] (optional fields) [plugin to create in]

What just happened

1. Created a controller
2. Created public folder structures

   vendor/plugins/[erp_app | plugin]/public/javascripts/erp_app/organizer/applications/[YOUR APP NAME]
   vendor/plugins/[erp_app | plugin]/public/stylesheets/erp_app/organizer/applications/[YOUR APP NAME]
   vendor/plugins/[erp_app | plugin]/public/images/erp_app/organizer/applications/[YOUR APP NAME]

3. Create a template for javascript class needed for organizer application
4. Created a data migration
5. Appended the routes file

Run the migration with

rake db:migrate_data

and start adding functionality



